import Sprite1 from "../../assets/sprites/lucas-walk-1-removebg-preview.png"; import Sprite2 from "../../assets/sprites/lucas-walk-2-removebg-preview.png"; import Sprite3 from "../../assets/sprites/lucas-walk-3-removebg-preview.png"; import "./PixelBanner.scss"; function PixelBanner({ banner }) { var pix = document.getElementsByClassName("pixel"); for (var i = 0; i < pix.length; i++) { pix[i].style.animationDelay = Math.random() * 5000 + "ms"; } const sprite = document.getElementById("sprite"); let counter = 1; setInterval(() => { counter++; console.log(counter); if (counter % 3 === 1) { sprite.setAttribute("src", Sprite1); } else if (counter % 3 === 2) { sprite.setAttribute("src", Sprite2); } else { sprite.setAttribute("src", Sprite3); } }, 1000); console.log(banner); return ( <>

{banner.toUpperCase()}

); } export default PixelBanner;
